---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Eliran Keren" description="Learn more about Eliran Keren">
  <article class="about-page">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <section>
      <h2>👋 Hello!</h2>
      <p>
        I'm Eliran, Founder and CEO of https://deeplica.ai  and I LOVE TO BUILD!.
        I love exploring new technologies, especially in the AI and automation space.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🛠️ What I Do</h2>
      <p>
        I build practical applications that combine modern web technologies with AI capabilities.
        My focus is on creating intuitive, performant solutions that make complex tasks simpler.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Full-stack web development</li>
        <li>AI integration and automation</li>
        <li>Developer tools and workflows</li>
        <li>Open-source contributions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🎯 Current Projects</h2>
      <p>
        I'm currently working on several exciting projects:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI Music Generator</strong> - A Suno-like application for creating music with AI</li>
        <li><strong>Claude Automation Toolkit</strong> - OpenClaw-inspired automation suite</li>
        <li><strong>This Blog</strong> - Sharing knowledge and experiences in tech</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>📫 Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Feel free to reach out if you want to collaborate, have questions, or just want to chat about tech!
      </p>
      <ul class="contact-links">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/Elirank1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:elirank512@gmail.com">Email</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .about-page h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-links a {
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
